          }
        }
      ],
      "flavor_text": "The healer vanishes through a wall of soft white dust, reappearing where the contagion is thickest \u2014 and the ground beneath their feet drinks deep, holding everything still. Chalk settles like a held breath."
    },
    {
      "id": "skill_000991",
